This paper involves the use of deep learning architectures for predicting the risk of readmission within 30 days of discharge from the ICU using electronic medical record data. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computational engineering, finance, and science (cs.CE), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and computational linguistics (cs.CL).
